## Flashing

Requires the <a href="https://www.aliexpress.com/item/1005002448932775.html?aff_fcid=c563b814adb848aa9ebe154b9d389aea-1652954042662-06297-_AUxjTz&tt=CPS_NORMAL&aff_fsk=_AUxjTz&aff_platform=shareComponent-detail&sk=_AUxjTz&aff_trace_key=c563b814adb848aa9ebe154b9d389aea-1652954042662-06297-_AUxjTz&terminal_id=5328bb0326ad4ecea39a5766fa327b23&afSmartRedirect=y">T-U2T Downloader</a> dongle for easiest flashing.

Flash using [Tasmota Web Installer](https://tasmota.github.io/install/) using **Tasmota** option.

